snippet.title: Road To Adventure! Announcement Trailer.
snippet.description:
Summer Vacation is here and the main problem is find a good way to spend it. So, you decide to embark on an adventure to bring down The Evil Corporation, and stop it from destroying the nearby forest that bring you so much happines and peace.
